        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: DGKθ is shown to primarily localize to Glut synapses (Fig.1E-G). Biochemical enrichment suggests localization to both pre- and postsynaptic compartments (Fig.D).. Experimental description: From personal communication with the author:\nWestern blot: mouse tissue\nImmunocytochem: rat neurons\n\n31/10/2017 Pim\n- Since pre post localization depends on panel D I make the annotation to the mouse species" ;
